<h1>Tutorial: Create IFrame Application</h1>
<div class="indent">
  <p>
    Very useful if you want to convert something you already made or don't want to use the OS.js API.
  </p>
  <pre class="code">
grunt create-package:default/MyPackageName:iframe
  </pre>

  <h2>Example code</h2>
  <p>
    In this example we have a simple directory called "data" inside the application with the file "index.html" where
    your code will be
  </p>
  <pre class="code">
function ApplicationExample(args, metadata) {
  Application.apply(this, ['ApplicationExample', args, metadata, {
    src: 'data/index.html',
    title: metadata.name,
    icon: metadata.icon,
    width: 640,
    height: 480,
    allow_resize: false,
    allow_restore: false,
    allow_maximize: false
  }]);
}
  </pre>

